Exaptation of I4760M mutation in ryanodine receptor of Spodoptera exigua 
(Lepidoptera: Noctuidae): Lessons from museum and field samples.

Han C(1), Rahman MM(2), Shin J(3), Kim JH(4), Lee SH(5), Kwon M(6), Timm AE(7), 
Ramasamy S(8), Lee Y(9), Kang S(10), Park S(11), Kim J(12).

Author information:
(1)Interdisciplinary Graduate Program in Smart Agriculture, Kangwon National 
Unversity, Chuncheon 24341, Republic of Korea. Electronic address: 
201711031@kangwon.ac.kr.
(2)Agriculture and Life Sciences Research Institute, Kangwon National 
