sjy0915ek@kangwon.ac.kr.
(4)Department of Tropical Medicine and Parasitology, Seoul National University, 
Seoul 03080, Republic of Korea. Electronic address: biomyst5@snu.ac.kr.
(5)Department of Agricultural Biotechnology, Seoul National University, Seoul 
08826, Republic of Korea. Electronic address: shlee22@snu.ac.kr.
(6)Department of Agricultural Biotechnology, Seoul National University, Seoul 
08826, Republic of Korea.
(7)Department of Agricultural Biology, Colorado State University, Fort Collins, 
CO 80523, USA. Electronic address: Alicia.Timm@colostate.edu.
(8)World Vegetable Center, Tainan, Taiwan. Electronic address: 
srini.ramasamy@worldveg.org.
(9)Gyeonggi Provincial Agricultural Research and Extension Services, Republic of 
Korea. Electronic address: yslee75@gg.go.kr.
(10)Highland Agriculture Research Institute, National Institute of Crop Science, 
Rural Development Administration, Pyeongchang, Republic of Korea. Electronic 
