Conventional physical therapy combined with extracorporeal shock wave leads to 
positive effects on spasticity in stroke survivors: a prospective observational 
study.

Mihai EE(1), Papathanasiou J(2), Panayotov K(3), Kashilska Y(4), Rosulescu E(5), 
